Ginny Baker was born with a skill for playing a game that, before her time, was considered a man s sport. The world of baseball is changed when Ginny is selected as the first woman to ever pitch in the Major League. She has to shoulder the responsibility of being a role model as the first woman in the sport, while dealing with the consequences of being the only female player in the league. Pitch is a revolutionary show that might be ahead of its time, but it is relevant because it has come at a time where people want to see change happen. Pitch is definitely one of the most riveting shows of 2016. Star Rating: 5/5